FBIS4-62095 "drsov092_b_94027" FBIS-SOV-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military & Nuclear Issues Civil Defense Exercises Begin in North Caucasus Civil Defense Exercises Begin in North Caucasus PM1105155194 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 11 May 94 First Edition p 1 PM1105155194 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [Report from ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA and ITAR-TASS column under the "Yesterday, Today, Tomorrow" rubric: "Command and Staff Exercises"] [Text] Command and staff exercises for [rehearsing] command and control of manpower and resources of the Russian Ministry for Civil Defense, Emergencies, and Natural Disasters in eliminating the consequences of natural disasters began on the territory of the North Caucasus yesterday. Civil defense troops and the ministry's central air-mobile detachment and search and rescue subunits are taking part in them.
